text.text: Very bad service from a public assistant called Silvia, she is always bitter with an attitude. I swore I will never visit that place. It lasted from 9 to 2 in the afternoon. A bipolar doctor, I had to tell her that we, the patients, are the ones. We paid for his office. I'm super angry. There are many places to go and with very good attention.
